{"problem":{"stackLimit":128,"modifiedUser":"root","auth":1,"isRemote":false,"description":"<p>为了获知基因序列在功能和结构上的相似性，经常需要将几条不同序列的DNA进行比对，以判断该比对的DNA是否具有相关性。<p><p>   现比对两条长度相同的DNA序列。定义两条DNA序列相同位置的碱基为一个碱基对，如果一个碱基对中的两个碱基相同的话，则称为相同碱基对。接着计算相同碱基对占总碱基对数量的比例，如果该比例大于等于给定阈值时则判定该两条DNA序列是相关的，否则不相关。<p>","removeEndBlank":true,"uploadCase":true,"source":"","remote":false,"title":"基因相关性 ","type":0,"difficulty":1,"output":"<p>若两条DNA序列相关，则输出“yes”，否则输出“no”。<p>","timeLimit":1000,"input":"<p>有三行，第一行是用来判定出两条DNA序列是否相关的阈值，随后2行是两条DNA序列(长度不大于500)。<p>","examples":"<input>0.85\nATCGCCGTAAGTAACGGTTTTAAATAGGCC\nATCGCCGGAAGTAACGGTCTTAAATAGGCC\n</input><output>yes\n</output>","ioScore":10000,"codeShare":false,"hint":"","isRemoveEndBlank":true,"openCaseResult":true,"memoryLimit":256,"problemId":"T1131","isUploadCase":true},"languages":["C","C With O2","C++","C++ With O2","Java","Python3","Python2","Golang","C#"],"codeTemplates":[],"isSpj":false,"samples":[{"output":"1.out","input":"1.in","score":100},{"output":"2.out","input":"2.in","score":100},{"output":"3.out","input":"3.in","score":100},{"output":"4.out","input":"4.in","score":100},{"output":"5.out","input":"5.in","score":100},{"output":"6.out","input":"6.in","score":100},{"output":"7.out","input":"7.in","score":100},{"output":"8.out","input":"8.in","score":100},{"output":"9.out","input":"9.in","score":100},{"output":"10.out","input":"10.in","score":100}],"tags":["一本通在线评测"]}